<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- lạ ạs̊ma yaḥ̊lū dẖik̊ruhu .. kās̊mi yasūʿa ạl̊masīḥ̊
 karĩrūhu ại̹nãhu .. kasẖadẖā ṭībiⁿ yafīḥ̊

[V2]
 2- bah̊jaẗu ạl̊qal̊bi bihi .. wāl̊ʿazāʾu wālsãlạm̊
 sabĩḥūhu ại̹nãhu .. bihi qad̊ zāla ạlẓãlạm̊

[V3]
 3- wās̊taqāma ạảm̊runā .. bihi wālrãẙbu ạn̊tafay̱
 majĩdūhu ại̹nãhu .. kulã daẙninā wafay̱

[V4]
 4- las̊tu ạảb̊gẖī gẖaẙrahu .. fah̊wa lī niʿ̊ma ạlnãṣīb̊
 ḥamĩdūhu ại̹nãhu .. rabũnā ạl̊fādī ạl̊ḥabīb̊

[V5]
 5- jāza fī ạảr̊ḍi ạlsẖãqā .. muẓ̊hiraⁿạ kulã kamāl̊
 ʿaẓĩmūhu wāq̊tafūạ .. ại̹tẖ̊ra man̊ ạảʿ̊ṭay̱ ạl̊mitẖāl̊

[V6]
 6- man̊ ạủhīna sayajī .. ʿan̊ qarībiⁿ lil̊jazā
 fatāảnũwạ tab̊lugẖūạ .. ạl̊maj̊da maʿ̊hu wāl̊munay̱</lyrics>
<title>lạ ạsm yḥlw dẖkrh</title>
</song>